// "You gain X% movement speed after pickup" (Mechanics, common). Installs the "bloom_movespeed"
// ActiveHooks flag, read by pickup/systems/collect_pickups.rs to apply the "bloom_swiftness"
// status. A boolean flag, so Exclusive despite the Common rarity (same shape as
// consecrated_ground_slow_common, Phase 9.3).
(
    id: "bloom_movespeed_common",
    display_name: "Blooming Swiftness",
    ability_scope: Some("bloom"),
    rarity: Common,
    uniqueness: Exclusive,
    effect: Behavior("bloom_movespeed"),
)
